{"tid":2380578,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中醫是安慰劑】專家：武肺病人如情況較嚴重，出現呼吸困難，不宜接受中醫治療","createTime":"2021-01-26T04:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T04:48:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1b233be1dcc0aa5e4e59a48f1b8719b692c63d","tid":2380578,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572387-20210126.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572387-20210126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BAVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=7bf6fab6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572387-20210126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3d5addfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572387-20210126.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局今日起在亞博館社區治療設施提供中醫診療服務。中大中醫學院副院長林志秀在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，如果病人情況較穩定，適合接受有關治療；如果情況較嚴重，例如出現呼吸困難則不適合。<br />\n<br />\n林志秀表示，如患者正服用西醫的抗病毒藥、肝腎較差、對中藥敏感或有蠶豆症，亦不適合接受有關中醫診療服務。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，根據內地文獻，患者接受有關中藥治療後，病毒由陽性轉陰性的時間由17天減至13天，住院日數由18天減至14天。"},{"pid":"102c088de64cc7cd0b3bdd91875eb08708aa141d","tid":2380578,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果病人情況較穩定，適合接受有關治療</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢D就唔醫都會自己好返啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食多個橙仲有意義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79882dba88b0c9bd836dafa60f04d59609d16431","tid":2380578,"uid":45498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T04:08:00.000Z","msg":"咁仲洗撚搵你咩垃圾神棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla